Run your Next.js application using `npm run dev` or `yarn dev`. Navigate to `http://localhost:3001/en/thanks?stripeCheckoutSessionId=cs_test_example` to see the page in action.

### Additional Notes
- Ensure your application handles the case where the `stripeCheckoutSessionId` might not be present in the URL.
- For production, replace `localhost:3001` with your actual domain.
- Consider adding styling or additional components to enhance the user experience.

